name: USD Coin Bridged NEDX from BNB
description: USDC.n is a USD-denominated asset within the NEDX ecosystem, designed for practical on-chain settlement and stable unit accounting across dApps. It is commonly used as a quote asset for trading pairs, liquidity pools, pricing references, and ecosystem payments. USDC.n emphasizes a consistent and predictable on-chain representation, enabling users and applications to exchange value efficiently across the NEDX network.
